relevant_findings.eyes: PERLLA (pupils equal, round, reactive to light and accommodation), EOMI (extraocular movements intact), no conjunctival injection, anicteric
relevant_findings.ENT: MM dry (mucous membranes dry), oropharynx without exudate or lesions, no supraclavicular or cervical lymphadenopathy
relevant_findings.respiratory: CTA b/l (clear to auscultation bilaterally) with good air movement throughout
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: RR (regular rhythm), S1 and S2 within normal limits, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops appreciated
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: nd (not distended), +b/s (positive bowel sounds), soft, tender in mid epigastrium, no rebound tenderness, JP drain in place with 30cc bilious fluid, incisions clean/dry/intact, no masses
relevant_findings.skin/nails: warm, no rashes, no jaundice, no splinters
relevant_findings.neurological: AAOx3 (alert, awake, oriented to person, place, and time), cranial nerves II-XII intact, strength throughout intact, fluent speech
